    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "先把显然不满足条件的特判掉。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "使用 <strong>+1/-1 前缀和</strong> 搞出来每个字符串的<strong>总和（收益/代价）k</strong>与<strong>拼接门槛 maxr</strong>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<em>（以下为<strong>贪心排序</strong>策略，排序没设计好很可能出现想当然的错误，上面的 EX 样例能判掉。）</em>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "先把<strong>有收益</strong>的那几个分为一组，即<strong>上山组（k >= 0）</strong>，按<strong>门槛升序</strong>和<strong>收益倒序</strong>来依次即可。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "然后就是要代价的<strong>下山组（k < 0）</strong>，因为收益已经全拿完了，为了保证这一组也能全拿完，自然想到<strong>先处理门槛高</strong>的，怕后面收益用完了处理不了门槛高的了。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "但光这样想过不了样例，门槛高的可能代价也很高，于是想到按照 <code>maxr + k</code> <strong>倒序</strong>排序，表示我们<strong>先处理门槛高且代价少</strong>的。这样处理，<strong>最次的情况</strong>下我们有门槛的水平，处理完后总收益为 <code>maxr + k</code> 还是大于等于后面的，所以肯定满足条件。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar p = vector<pii>(n + 1);\n\tint tot = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tstring s; cin >> s;\n\t\tint k = 0, maxr = 0; // 总和，门槛\n\t\tfor (char c : s) {\n\t\t\tif (c == '(')k++;\n\t\t\telse k--;\n\t\t\tmaxr = max(maxr, -k);\n\t\t}\n\t\tp[i] = { maxr,k };\n\t\ttot += k;\n\t}\n\n\tif (tot != 0) {\n\t\tcout << \"No\" << endl;\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\n\tsort(all1(p), [](const var& a, const var& b)->bool {\n\t\tif (a.py < 0 and b.py < 0)return a.px + a.py > b.px + b.py; // 门槛高且代价少\n\t\telse if (a.py < 0)return 0;\n\t\telse if (b.py < 0)return 1;\n\t\telse {\n\t\t\tif (a.px == b.px)return a.py > b.py;\n\t\t\treturn a.px < b.px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t});\n\n\tint k = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tconst var& [maxr, nk] = p[i];\n\t\tif (k >= maxr) {\n\t\t\tk += nk;\n\t\t\tif (k < 0) {\n\t\t\t\tcout << \"No\" << endl;\n\t\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t\telse {\n\t\t\tcout << \"No\" << endl;\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tif (k == 0)cout << \"Yes\" << endl;\n\telse cout << \"No\" << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
